en_182662_0	Six persons are reported to have attacked a grade 10 teacher for punishing a student.
en_182662_1	The persons had forcibly entered Aalankuda Muslim School in Kalpitiya and attacked the teacher, who was thereafter admitted to hospital with injuries.
en_182662_2	The Norochcholai Police arrested the father of the student, who was punished by the teacher, for assaulting the teacher.
en_182662_3	The other 5 suspects are yet to be arrested.
en_182662_4	The victimized teacher has told police that the student was punished for making inappropriate jokes to female students.
